metadata.name: Interconnected
metadata.description:
What meaning do humans place in materials and empty space? 
What is it at all and what role does it play in the theories of physics? 
How do we feel ourselves in space?

The artist works with the digital materials gold, ultramarine blue and glass to deal with these questions. 
She chose these materials and flowing representation because they have to do with her own experience. 
She uses them to treat the healing process of her cancer. 

The representation should allow an open interpretation. 

Size: 4482 × 4482

Created 29 August 2022
